ntil-next-year/?sh=4db57994dec4|accessdate=2021-04-07|date=2020-11-15|archivedate=2021-04-13|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210413105332/https://www.forbes.com/sites/olliebarder/2020/11/15/the-first-gundam-hathaways-flash-movie-has-had-its-release-delayed-until-next-year/?sh=4db57994dec4|last=Barder|first=Ollie|work=[[福布斯|福布斯]]|language=en|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

