E%E5%93%88%E6%92%92%E7%BB%B4%E7%9A%84%E9%97%AA%E5%85%89%7C%E9%98%BF%E5%A7%86%E7%BD%97%7C%E9%97%AA%E5%85%89%E7%9A%84%E5%93%88%E8%90%A8%E7%BB%B4%7C%E5%93%88%E8%90%A8%E7%BB%B4_%E6%96%B0%E6%B5%AA%E6%96%B0%E9%97%BB&ari=2&ver=0916&dbv=2&drs=1&pcs=994x13653&pss=1000x14134&cfv=0&cpl=3&chi=50&cce=true&cec=UTF-8&tlm=1631868813&prot=2&rw=320&ltu=http%3A%2F%2Fk.sina.com.cn%2Farticle_1893905030_70e2b28600100yo6u.html&liu=http%3A%2F%2Fk.sina.com.cn%2Farticle_1893905030_70e2b28600100yo6u.html&ecd=1&uc=1600x1000&pis=300x250&sr=1600x1000&tcn=1631868814&qn=73d072d0697c56d2&tt=1631868813553.16.828.830&lto=http%3A%2F%2Fk.sina.com.cn&ltl=1|archive-date=2021-09-17}}</ref>。[[Bangumi|Bangumi]]上本片的评分为8.3分，推荐力度为“力荐”<ref>{{Cite web|title=《闪光的哈萨维》第二部副标题已经确定，剧情大改？|url=https://www.163.com/dy/article/GJ62RM6Q0515A574.html|access-date=2021-09-16|date=2021-09-06|last=网易|work=网易|language=zh-cn|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210916080805/https://www.163.com/dy/article/GJ62RM6Q0515A574.html|archive-date=2021-09-16}}</ref>。评价集中在其人物和机甲画面的高制作水准，盛赞其CG与手绘表现，背景图像的精致，场景表现的写实感<ref>{{Cite web|title=全球首发！《机动战士高达闪光的哈萨维》观后心得|url=https://www.163.com/dy/article/GC97N8T40515A574.html|access-date=2021-06-13|date=2021-06-12|last=网易|work=网易|language=zh-cn|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210613064645/https://www.163.com/dy/article/GC97N8T40515A574.html|archive-date=2021-06-13|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":69">{{Cite web|title=五星好评的《闪光的哈萨维》，好看在哪里？|url=https://new.qq.com/omn/20210613/20210613A008XM00.html|access-date=2021-06-13|date=2021-06-13|work=腾讯新闻|language=zh-cn|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210624194848/https://new.qq.com/omn/20210613/20210613A008XM00.html|archive-date=2021-06-24|dead-url=no}}</ref>。而缺点则主要偏向于人物刻画与剧情结构经过压缩相比原著小说有所不足、战斗桥段画面表现偏暗导致机动战士的细节不易看清<ref name=":69" />。动漫新闻网的理查德·艾森贝-{}-斯（Richard Eisenbeis）将本片评价为B，“质感很漂亮但受限于制作过程中的一些创造性的选择”，并批评其整体情节说“动画改编中采用了多种技巧，但比起这些更应当去体现其原著的本来面貌。”<ref>{{cite web|title=Mobile Suit Gundam Hathaway|url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/review/mobile-suit-gundam-hathaway/.171929|access-date=2021-07-09|date=2021-04-24|last=Eisenbeis|first=Richard|website=動畫新聞網|archive-date=2021-10-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211029014421/https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/review/mobile-suit-gundam-hathaway/.171929|dead-url=no}}</ref>

